high_descs: Move to the table with the coffee machine.
Pick up the fork on the table.
Bring the fork to the sink.
Wash the fork in the sink.
Bring the cleaned fork to the table with the coffee machine.
Put the cleaned fork on the table next to the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned fork on the table next to the potato.

high_descs: Move to the right side of the kitchen table across from the sink in front of the window
Pick up fork from off the kitchen table
Move to the sink across the room from the table
Place fork in the sink and turn on the water for a moment before turning it off and picking the fork back up
Move to the kitchen table behind you in front of the window
Place fork on to the table
anns.task_desc: Clean and replace the fork on the kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn around until your facing the wall by the table. Walk to the wall and turn left to look down at the table.
Pick up the fork on the table.
Turn to the left facing the sink and walk towards it.
Put the fork in the sink on the left. Turn on the water and then turn it off. Pick up the fork out of the sink.
Turn around and go back to the table.
Put the fork back on the table flipped over.
anns.task_desc: Clean a fork to put it on the table.
